提供代写代读服务
Anything written! Anything read!


442
00:35:33.470 --> 00:35:35.710
之前在这摆摊的男人呢？
What happened to the man who used to sit here?


443
00:35:37.010 --> 00:35:39.070
这问题很好答吧
It is a simple question.


444
00:35:39.070 --> 00:35:40.910
你难道不知道吗？
Don't you know?


445
00:35:40.910 --> 00:35:43.840
我怎么会知道？回答问题 他在哪？
How should I know? Answer the question. Where is he?


446
00:35:43.840 --> 00:35:47.010
- 他去马扎里沙里夫了 - 那你又是他的什么人？
- He left for Mazar-e-Sharif. - And what are you to him?


447
00:35:47.010 --> 00:35:51.520
我是他的外甥 我叫..奥狄什
I'm his nephew, uh... Aatish.


448
00:35:53.550 --> 00:35:55.450
你认字吗？
Do you know how to read?


449
00:35:55.460 --> 00:35:59.490
- 你有什么要我读的？我会普什图语和达利语 - 读读这个
- Do you have something to read? I read Pashto and Dari. - Read this.


450
00:36:02.730 --> 00:36:04.770
让我见识下你的水平
Let's see if you're any good.


451
00:36:11.470 --> 00:36:13.840
快点 把信拿出来
Come on. Take it out of the envelope.


452
00:36:16.180 --> 00:36:17.780
“亲爱的拉扎克……”
"Dear Razaq..."


453
00:36:17.780 --> 00:36:20.780
大声点 不然我去叫别人读了
Louder, or I will have to take my business elsewhere.


454
00:36:20.780 --> 00:36:24.180
“亲爱的拉扎克 我希望在喀布尔的你能收到这封信
"Dear Razaq, I hope this letter reaches you in Kabul.


455
00:36:24.190 --> 00:36:27.190
我写信给你 是想告知你一个不好的消息
I'm writing to you with sad news.


456
00:36:27.190 --> 00:36:32.430
很遗憾地告诉你 哈拉·贝格姆在去她妹妹婚礼的路上去世了
I am sorry to tell you that Hala Begum died on the way to her sister's wedding.


457
00:36:33.660 --> 00:36:37.100
她坐的那辆巴士碰到了地雷
The bus she was traveling on hit a land mine.


458
00:36:37.100 --> 00:36:39.530
她受了重伤 难以救治
Her injuries were too great to bear


459
00:36:39.530 --> 00:36:41.900
几小时之后便去世了
and she died some hours afterward.


460
00:36:41.900 --> 00:36:44.540
我知道这对你来说必定是天大的打击
I know this must be a great shock to you,


461
00:36:44.540 --> 00:36:46.870
但我要跟你说 在我最后一次和哈拉的谈话中
but please know that when I last spoke to Hala,


462
00:36:46.880 --> 00:36:49.580
她告诉我说你对她真的很好
she told me of your kindness toward her.


463
00:36:51.080 --> 00:36:53.180
愿真主安拉保佑你
May Allah bless you now,


464
00:36:53.180 --> 00:36:55.820
指引你道路 给予你勇气”
guide your path, and give you courage."


465
00:36:59.150 --> 00:37:00.920
节哀顺变
I'm sorry.


466
00:37:33.550 --> 00:37:36.560
我亲爱的宝贝
Ah, there's my sweet little girl


467
00:37:36.560 --> 00:37:38.260
脸上全是喀布尔的灰尘
underneath all the dust of Kabul.


468
00:37:39.990 --> 00:37:42.590
帕尔瓦娜 你给扎西什么了？
Parvana, what did you give Zaki?


469
00:37:42.600 --> 00:37:44.860
- 1块糖 - 1整块？
- It's a piece of candy. - A piece?


470
00:37:44.870 --> 00:37:47.070
喔
Oh!


471
00:37:47.070 --> 00:37:49.540
太大了 他噎着了
It's big enough to choke him!


472
00:37:49.540 --> 00:37:52.270
他没事的 苏拉娅 你坏他兴子呢
Let him be, Soraya. You're spoiling his fun.


473
00:37:53.970 --> 00:37:55.280
嗷
Ow!


474
00:37:55.280 --> 00:37:58.180
继续讲吧 帕尔瓦娜
Continue the story, Parvana.


475
00:37:58.180 --> 00:38:00.310
讲给扎西听
For Zaki.


476
00:38:00.320 --> 00:38:02.750
很久很久以前 有一位年轻的小男孩
There was this young boy,


477
00:38:02.750 --> 00:38:07.320
他向村民发誓 要去找到那袋珍贵的种子
and he promised his people to find the precious seeds.


