Anything written! Anything read!


644
00:50:15.520 --> 00:50:17.520
上次我没付钱
I didn't pay you last time.


645
00:50:17.520 --> 00:50:20.350
- 该给你多少？ - 没关系的 呃...
- How much do I owe you? - It's okay. I...


646
00:50:20.350 --> 00:50:22.590
怎么 坏消息就不收费吗？
What, you don't charge for bad news?


647
00:50:27.730 --> 00:50:30.330
是谁教你识字的？那个残疾的老师吗？
Who taught you to read? The crippled teacher?


648
00:50:30.330 --> 00:50:32.060
嗯 他是我叔叔
Yes. My uncle.


649
00:50:32.070 --> 00:50:34.530
你写信跟读信一样厉害吗？
Can you write as good as you read?


650
00:50:34.530 --> 00:50:35.800
我可以的
I can.


651
00:50:37.710 --> 00:50:39.370
瞧
Here.


652
00:50:41.940 --> 00:50:44.510
我觉得你可能会要回这封信 所以就一直留着呢
I kept this in case you wanted it.


653
00:50:45.610 --> 00:50:48.050
告诉我 告诉我哪处是她的名字
Show me. Show me where it says her name.


654
00:50:48.050 --> 00:50:50.520
哪写了“哈拉”
Where it says "Hala."


655
00:50:52.620 --> 00:50:54.420
那儿 看到了吗？
There. See?


656
00:50:55.090 --> 00:50:56.720
哈拉
Hala.


657
00:51:14.510 --> 00:51:16.880
你知道哈拉是什么意思吗？
Do you know what it means?


658
00:51:16.880 --> 00:51:18.550
不知道
No.


659
00:51:19.780 --> 00:51:23.680
有时候 在你透过晴朗的夜空看月亮时
Sometimes, on a clear night when you look at the moon,


660
00:51:23.680 --> 00:51:26.350
能看到月亮被一条明亮的光圈围绕着
you can see a bright outline around it.


661
00:51:27.590 --> 00:51:30.990
那条光圈就叫作哈拉
That outline is called hala.


662
00:51:30.990 --> 00:51:34.430
我妻子以它来取名
My wife was named for that light.


663
00:51:43.600 --> 00:51:45.400
- 给你 - 这太多了
- Here. - This is too much.


664
00:51:45.410 --> 00:51:47.640
别推辞
Don't argue with me.


665
00:51:47.640 --> 00:51:48.880
谢谢你
Thank you.


666
00:52:00.450 --> 00:52:04.120
好啦 扎西 我可以揪你的吗？
Stop it, Zaki. Can I pull yours?


667
00:52:06.160 --> 00:52:08.990
让他安静点 我还想睡觉呢
Keep him quiet. I'm trying to sleep.


668
00:52:09.000 --> 00:52:12.900
- 你犯什么毛病呢？ - 要不你给扎西讲个故事吧 好不好？
- What's the matter with you? - Why don't you tell Zaki a story, hmm?


669
00:52:12.900 --> 00:52:14.600
我们都很喜欢
We'd all like that.


670
00:52:14.600 --> 00:52:17.970
好吧 扎西 你想听故事里的小男孩后来怎么样了吗？
Well, Zaki, do you want to know what happened to the boy?


671
00:52:19.670 --> 00:52:21.940
好的 好的 还有大象
Yes, yes, and the elephant.


672
00:52:23.510 --> 00:52:27.810
男孩跑啊跑 他很害怕 心跳得特别快
The boy ran and ran, his heart beating fast in fear.


673
00:52:27.820 --> 00:52:30.980
身后追逐他的东西丝毫没有停下的意思
And the thing that chased him never stopped.


674
00:52:33.750 --> 00:52:37.560
于是小男孩非常害怕地躲在树后
So the boy hid behind a tree and he waited for courage.


675
00:52:44.930 --> 00:52:48.170
一位老妇人想要挤山羊奶
An ancient woman had been trying to milk a goat,


676
00:52:48.170 --> 00:52:50.600
可她后背酸痛难忍
but her back was very sore.


677
00:52:50.600 --> 00:52:56.040
我的背好痛啊
My back is very sore.


678
00:52:56.040 --> 00:53:00.680
男孩很同情老妇人 于是让老妇人在树荫下休息
The boy took pity on her and told her to rest under the shade of a tree


679
00:53:00.680 --> 00:53:02.750
他来挤羊奶
and he would do the milking instead.


680
00:53:02.750 --> 00:53:04.850
您到树荫下坐着吧
Please sit under the shade of this tree,


681
00:53:04.850 --> 00:53:07.520
我来帮您挤
and I will do the milking instead.


682
00:53:14.760 --> 00:53:16.800
当他挤完羊奶后
When he finished milking the goat,


683
00:53:16.800 --> 00:53:19.900
老妇人与他分享美味又温暖的羊奶
the old woman shared the lovely, warm milk with him.


684
00:53:19.900 --> 00:53:23.870
这是他喝过最好喝的羊奶
It was the nicest milk he had ever tasted,


685
00:53:23.870 --> 00:53:26.540
于是他称赞老了妇人的羊群
and he complimented the woman on her goats.


686
00:53:26.540 --> 00:53:28.740
您山羊的产奶量真多
Your goats are very generous.


687
00:53:28.740 --> 00:53:31.980
老妇人给男孩一面镜子作为回报
In return, the old woman gave him a mirror.


688
00:53:31.980 --> 00:53:36.180
看 多闪啊
See how it shines!


689
00:53:36.180 --> 00:53:38.680
得到镜子后 男孩非常高兴
The boy was delighted with the mirror,


690
00:53:38.690 --> 00:53:43.790
但他看着镜子时 镜子照出了尾随他的东西
but as he looked into it, he saw the reflection of the thing that followed him!


691
00:53:48.090 --> 00:53:49.760
妈妈 你在做什么？
What are you doing, Mama-jan?


692
00:53:49.760 --> 00:53:52.560
我在收拾苏拉娅的衣服
I'm laying out Soraya's good clothes.


693
00:53:52.570 --> 00:53:54.900
这些衣服要我拿到市场去卖吗？
Am I to sell them at the market?


694
00:53:54.900 --> 00:53:57.910
嘘 帕尔瓦娜 该睡觉了
Shh, shh, shh, Parvana. It's time to sleep.


695
00:54:06.050 --> 00:54:09.680
我得想方设法去白沙瓦
I just need to find a way to get to Peshawar,


696
00:54:09.680 --> 00:54:11.820
在那里我会计划出属于我的未来
and I can figure it out from there.


697
00:54:11.820 --> 00:54:14.220
我想果阿会有海滩
I think there's a beach in Goa


698
00:54:14.220 --> 00:54:16.590
那的游客非常富有
where the tourists are very rich.


699
00:54:16.590 --> 00:54:18.790
如果他们有钱 那我的蓝色石头就能卖出去了
If they're rich, they would buy my blue stones,


700
00:54:18.790 --> 00:54:22.130
在那我就能经营我的小生意了 届时你就可以跟我合伙干了
and that's where I'd set up my business, and you could join me.


701
00:54:22.130 --> 00:54:24.260
在我找到爸爸后
Once I find Baba.


702
00:54:24.260 --> 00:54:26.600
嗯 在你找到你爸爸后
Once you find your Baba.


703
00:54:45.850 --> 00:54:47.150
100

704
00:54:47.150 --> 00:54:48.650
85呗
I'll give you 85.


705
00:54:48.660 --> 00:54:49.890
- 90最低 - 82怎么样
- Ninety. - Eighty-two.


706
00:54:49.890 --> 00:54:51.890
最少85了
Eighty-five, and that's final.


707
00:54:51.890 --> 00:54:54.530
再加上一串葡萄 就这么定了
Eighty-five and a bunch of grapes, and that's final.


708
00:54:59.300 --> 00:55:03.770
你写字下笔太重了 但字写得不错
You're leaning too hard on the pen, but your writing is good.


709
00:55:03.770 --> 00:55:06.540
如果你再温柔一点 写好字会更容易些
If you try it more gently, it'll be easier.


710
00:55:43.340 --> 00:55:45.710
等等 请等一下
Wait! Wait a moment!


711
00:55:47.350 --> 00:55:49.210
什么事？
What is it, child?


712
00:55:49.220 --> 00:55:52.920
你曾问过我之前坐在我身边的那...那个老师的情况
You asked me before about the man who used to sit there... the teacher.


713
00:55:52.920 --> 00:55:56.050
- 你叔叔？ - 他不是去了马扎里沙里夫
- Your uncle? - He didn't go to Mazar-e-Sharif.


714
00:55:56.060 --> 00:55:59.220
我叔叔进了监狱 然而他是冤枉的
He was taken to prison. But he did nothing wrong.


715
00:55:59.230 --> 00:56:00.790
- 哪一个？ - 什么哪一个？
- Which one? - What?


716
00:56:00.790 --> 00:56:03.090
- 哪所监狱？ - 普利查西监狱
- Which prison? - Pul-e-Charkhi.


717
00:56:03.100 --> 00:56:06.630
已经过了几个星期了 但仍就杳无音信
It's been weeks now, and my family has had no word of him.


718
00:56:08.700 --> 00:56:10.670
星期三去监狱一趟吧
Go to the prison on Wednesday.


719
00:56:10.670 --> 00:56:12.340
去找我表弟罗尚帮忙
Ask for Roshan. He's my cousin.


720
00:56:12.340 --> 00:56:15.910
告诉他是拉扎克让你来的 他力所能及的话 就会帮你的
Tell him Razaq sent you and he will help you, if he can.


721
00:56:42.340 --> 00:56:43.740
德利瓦
Deliwar!


722
00:56:43.740 --> 00:56:49.240
照这样干下去 等我到海边的那天 我都变成风烛残年的老太太了
With work like this, I'll be an old woman by the time I get to the sea.


723
00:56:49.240 --> 00:56:52.080
或是个老头儿
Or an old man.


724
00:56:57.280 --> 00:57:01.390
你坐着休息下 我给你讲个故事
You sit and rest, Deliwar, and I'll tell you a story.


725
00:57:01.390 --> 00:57:04.660
- 故事？ - 对呀
- A story? - Yes, a story.


726
00:57:05.760 --> 00:57:07.320
在很久很久以前
One time in the deep past,


727
00:57:07.330 --> 00:57:11.900
从前有一个小男孩 他要把怪物偷走的袋子带回到村里 袋子里装着的是十分珍贵的种子
there was a boy who had to return a stolen bag of precious seeds to his village.


728
00:57:11.900 --> 00:57:15.330
是个喜剧吗 还是...悲剧呢？
Is it a happy story or a sad story?


729
00:57:15.340 --> 00:57:17.640
你听完就知道了
Just wait and see.


730
00:57:18.970 --> 00:57:22.010
男孩得知 必须集齐三件事物
The boy had been told he needed three things


731
00:57:22.010 --> 00:57:25.180
才能战胜象王
in order to overcome the Elephant King...


732
00:57:25.180 --> 00:57:29.050
一件闪着光 一件用来抓捕的 和...
something that shines, something that ensnares and something that...


733
00:57:29.050 --> 00:57:31.920
喂 你们两个 过来
Hey, you two! Come here!


734
00:57:33.290 --> 00:57:35.120
来啊
Come on!


735
00:57:35.120 --> 00:57:36.720
我认识他
I know that boy.


736
00:57:36.720 --> 00:57:39.260
快点 马上过来
Hurry up. Come here.


737
00:57:39.260 --> 00:57:40.890
快点啊
Come on.


738
00:57:40.890 --> 00:57:43.700
我们最好听他的话过去
We'd better do what we're told.


739
00:57:46.800 --> 00:57:48.840
赶快啊 懒鬼
Get a move on, lazy kids.


740
00:57:57.040 --> 00:57:59.080
这就是新来的苦力？
So these are the new workers?


741
00:57:59.080 --> 00:58:01.950
快回答啊 你们是傻子吗？
Where are your tongues? Are you stupid?


742
00:58:01.950 --> 00:58:05.150
伊德瑞斯提议用掰手腕的方式来做个小测验
Idrees suggested we have a little arm-wrestling match.


743
00:58:06.150 --> 00:58:09.250
看看你们是否有资格为我工作
To see if you're strong enough to work for me.


744
00:58:09.260 --> 00:58:11.890
我看到你坐在那儿偷懒
I saw you sitting down over there instead of working.


745
00:58:11.890 --> 00:58:13.890
停下 伊德瑞斯
Idrees, stop now.


746
00:58:13.890 --> 00:58:15.860
给我来杯茶水
Make me some tea.


747
00:58:19.830 --> 00:58:22.770
小不点 让我见识下你有多废物
Let me see how feeble you are, little one.


748
00:58:24.040 --> 00:58:26.310
这弱鸡连手都抬不起来
He can't even lift his hand.


749
00:58:27.940 --> 00:58:30.240
起来吧 端点茶水来
Get up and make us tea.


750
00:58:31.510 --> 00:58:34.980
叔叔 我觉得你需要招新工人了
Uncle, I think you need new workers.


751
00:58:34.980 --> 00:58:37.850
- 这两个简直太废了 - 够了 伊德瑞斯
- These ones are no good. - Enough, Idrees.


752
00:58:37.850 --> 00:58:39.480
别难为这些可怜的娃了
Leave the poor kids alone.


753
00:58:39.490 --> 00:58:41.990
他们俩还是太嫩
They are a little undercooked.


754
00:58:45.830 --> 00:58:48.130
我知道你
I know you.


755
00:58:48.130 --> 00:58:50.330
你是那个老师的女...
You're the teacher's daugh...


756
00:58:55.800 --> 00:58:57.940
伊德瑞斯
Idrees.


757
00:58:57.940 --> 00:58:59.940
把枪拿回来
Bring the gun back!


758
00:58:59.940 --> 00:59:01.970
我说了 把枪拿回来
I said bring the gun back!


759
00:59:01.970 --> 00:59:04.880
伊德瑞斯
Idrees!


760
00:59:23.300 --> 00:59:25.100
滚出来
Come out now!


761
00:59:28.440 --> 00:59:30.470
给我滚出来
Come out now!


762
00:59:30.470 --> 00:59:33.770
伊德瑞斯 战争已经开始了 我们要向西转移
Idrees, it has begun! We are moving west.


763
00:59:34.840 --> 00:59:37.610
我们接到命令要立刻行动
We have been given orders to go immediately!


764
00:59:37.610 --> 00:59:39.840
我知道你是谁
I know who you are!


765
00:59:39.850 --> 00:59:41.350
你听见了吗？
Do you hear?


766
00:59:42.450 --> 00:59:44.550
快上来 快
Get up here! Come on!


767
00:59:46.290 --> 00:59:48.920
现在就上来 你个怂包
Right now! You little coward!


768
00:59:50.960 --> 00:59:54.930
你不是想参战吗？ 现在你的机会来了
You want to fight? Now is your chance to fight!


769
00:59:56.900 --> 00:59:58.300
做个男人吧
You become a man.


770
01:00:21.260 --> 01:00:23.550
他走了
He's gone.


771
01:00:23.560 --> 01:00:25.620
他要是回来了呢？
What if he comes back?


772
01:00:25.630 --> 01:00:27.930
那只能算他运气好
He'd be lucky.


773
01:00:27.930 --> 01:00:29.490
我们这是在哪？
Where are we?


774
01:00:29.500 --> 01:00:31.900
我逃跑时候来过这里一次
I came here once when I ran away.


775
01:00:31.900 --> 01:00:35.970
不知道是我身体长大了 还是进来的洞口变窄了
I think the way in has gotten smaller or I have gotten bigger.


776
01:00:36.670 --> 01:00:38.440
这东西看起来有点历史了
It looks old.


777
01:00:39.340 --> 01:00:41.010
我丢了一只鞋
I lost a shoe.


778
01:00:41.010 --> 01:00:44.510
我帽子也丢了 可我觉得它就在外面
I lost my cap, although I think it's outside.


779
01:00:44.510 --> 01:00:46.350
你为什么揍他？
Why did you hit him?


780
01:00:48.920 --> 01:00:51.420
把我爸绑走的那伙人里有他一个
When they took my father, he was one of them.


781
01:00:53.550 --> 01:00:55.290
再给我讲讲那个男孩吧
Tell me more about the boy.


782
01:00:55.290 --> 01:00:56.990
什么男孩？
What boy?


783
01:00:56.990 --> 01:00:58.960
故事里的那个男孩
The story boy.


784
01:00:58.960 --> 01:01:01.690
男孩觉得很冷
The boy was cold.


785
01:01:01.690 --> 01:01:05.300
虽然太阳挂在空中 他却感受不到一丝温暖
Though the sun burned in the sky, it gave no heat.


786
01:01:05.300 --> 01:01:08.300
但是他有一个又大又暖的外套
But he had a warm hat and a big coat.


787
01:01:08.300 --> 01:01:10.030
不 他没有
No, he didn't.


788
01:01:10.040 --> 01:01:12.500
他已经发现三件事物中的一件了...
He had already found one of the three things...


789
01:01:12.510 --> 01:01:14.410
一个闪光的镜子
a mirror that shone.


790
01:01:14.410 --> 01:01:18.040
但是当他往镜子里看时 他看到了他身后的东西
But when he looked at it, he saw something behind him.


791
01:01:18.050 --> 01:01:20.710
那东西很吓人 非常恐怖
Something scary. Something dreadful!


792
01:01:20.710 --> 01:01:23.680
- 是一匹马 - 不 什沃吉亚 不是一匹马
- A horse! - No, Shauzia, not a horse.


793
01:01:23.680 --> 01:01:25.580
是啊 就是一匹马
Yes, it was.


794
01:01:25.590 --> 01:01:29.190
还是一匹非常老的马 走起路来骨头都咔哒咔哒响
And it was a very old horse whose bones clattered together when it walked.


795
01:01:29.190 --> 01:01:32.420
这一点都不吓人
It wasn't scary at all.


796
01:01:32.430 --> 01:01:36.730
好吧  看到老马的样子 男孩感到很难过 于是他喂了它一些干草
Fine. The boy felt sad for the old horse and fed him hay.


797
01:01:36.730 --> 01:01:38.700
然后他们都过上了幸福的生活
And they all lived happily ever after.


798
01:01:38.700 --> 01:01:41.430
我才讲到故事的一半 这不是结局
It's the middle of the story, not the end!


799
01:01:41.440 --> 01:01:44.200
从一个石室的门里
From a door carved into the stone,


800
01:01:44.200 --> 01:01:46.500
走出来一个胖子
out came a round man.


801
01:01:46.510 --> 01:01:50.570
你竟然把我的干草浪费在一匹即将死去的老马身上
You wasted my hay on an old horse that will soon be dead!


802
01:01:50.580 --> 01:01:53.680
胖子把男孩扔进了一口古井的深处
The round man threw the boy deep into the belly of an ancient well.


803
01:01:53.680 --> 01:01:56.280
啊..
Aaah!


804
01:01:57.550 --> 01:02:00.180
在井的底部有绿宝石
At the bottom of the well there were emeralds,


805
01:02:00.190 --> 01:02:04.260
胖子想让男孩把绿宝石拿给他 作为男孩浪费干草的补偿
and the round man wanted them brought up to him as payment for the wasted hay.


806
01:02:04.260 --> 01:02:06.620
你得把那些绿宝石拿给我
You will bring the emeralds to me.


807
01:02:06.630 --> 01:02:08.660
- 他的名字是？ - 你问的是那个胖子的？
- What's his name? - The round man?


808
01:02:08.660 --> 01:02:10.430
不是 是那个男孩的名字
No, the boy.


809
01:02:10.430 --> 01:02:13.660
你不能光讲人家男孩的故事 不给人家起个名字
You can't have a story about a boy and not give him a name.


810
01:02:13.670 --> 01:02:15.600
你不起我可要给他起名字了啊
Give him a name before I do.


811
01:02:15.600 --> 01:02:17.470
苏莱曼
Sulayman.


812
01:02:17.470 --> 01:02:19.970
他叫苏莱曼
His name is Sulayman.


813
01:02:20.610 --> 01:02:22.440
这是个好名字
That's a good name.


814
01:02:22.440 --> 01:02:25.410
苏莱曼倒在井的底部
Sulayman lay at the bottom of the well.


815
01:02:25.410 --> 01:02:28.510
突然 他看到了几具骷髅
Suddenly, he could see skeletons.


816
01:02:28.510 --> 01:02:33.350
一共3具骷髅 它们的骨手里都攥着一颗绿宝石
Three skeletons, each with an emerald clutched in its bony hands.


817
01:02:33.350 --> 01:02:35.190
- 他大声呼救 - 救命
- He called out for help. - Help!


818
01:02:35.190 --> 01:02:38.320
那匹可怜的老马从井口向下望着他
The poor old horse looked back at him from way above.


819
01:02:38.320 --> 01:02:41.230
然后它做了一件很神奇的事情
But the horse did something extraordinary.


820
01:02:41.230 --> 01:02:44.160
它发出了世界上所有种动物的叫声
He neighed with the voice of all the world's animals.


821
01:02:53.810 --> 01:02:57.110
苏莱曼爬啊爬 终于爬到了井的顶部
Sulayman climbed up, up, all the way to the top,


822
01:02:57.110 --> 01:02:59.480
然后他对救他一命的老马表示了感谢
and he thanked the horse for saving his life.


823
01:02:59.480 --> 01:03:02.320
谢谢你救了我的命
Thank you for saving my life.


824
01:03:07.190 --> 01:03:09.650
苏莱曼拿到了那三块宝石
Sulayman had just three emeralds with him...


825
01:03:09.660 --> 01:03:12.660
于是他要求胖子用食物来换
And asked the round man for food in return.


826
01:03:12.660 --> 01:03:14.390
他很饿
He was hungry.


827
01:03:14.390 --> 01:03:16.660
但那胖子即卑鄙又很小气
But the round man was wicked and cheap.


828
01:03:16.660 --> 01:03:20.530
他扔给了苏莱曼一个渔网 让他自己捕鱼吃
He threw a fishing net at Sulayman and he told him to get his own food.


829
01:03:20.530 --> 01:03:23.800
- 这网正是苏莱曼所需之物 - 哈哈
- That was exactly what Sulayman needed. - Ha-ha!


830
01:03:23.800 --> 01:03:26.200
那件用来抓捕的事物
Something that ensnares.


831
01:03:26.210 --> 01:03:27.810
但在苏莱曼的离开后
But as Sulayman left,


832
01:03:27.810 --> 01:03:31.540
三具骷髅的鬼魂从宝石里出来了
the ghosts of the three skeletons came out of the three emeralds


833
01:03:31.550 --> 01:03:34.510
它们在胖子头上缠转盘旋 吓得胖子魂不附体
and swirled and twirled and scared the round man


834
01:03:34.510 --> 01:03:37.820
用如此手段来向害他们丧命的胖子复仇
in frightful vengeance for having lost them their lives.


835
01:03:42.090 --> 01:03:45.720
苏莱曼和那匹老马继续向山那边进发
Sulayman and the horse continued their journey toward the mountain,


836
01:03:45.720 --> 01:03:49.230
但老马越走越慢了
but the horse was getting slower and slower.


837
01:03:49.230 --> 01:03:52.600
它实在是太老了 需要休息
He needed to rest, being very, very old,


838
01:03:52.600 --> 01:03:55.500
于是苏莱曼为它搭了一个帐篷
and so Sulayman made a shelter for the horse


839
01:03:55.500 --> 01:03:58.200
然后让这匹马等他回来
and told him to wait for him.


840
01:03:58.210 --> 01:04:00.570
那匹马有意阻止男孩...
The horse protested...


841
01:04:00.570 --> 01:04:04.510
但苏莱曼知道 象王和它的爪牙
but Sulayman knew he had to face the Elephant King and the jaguars


842
01:04:04.510 --> 01:04:06.140
他必须亲自去面对
all by himself.


843
01:04:06.150 --> 01:04:08.180
我们会再见面的 老伙计
I will see you again, old horse.


844
01:04:10.380 --> 01:04:12.450
说完他就一个人上路了
And so on he went alone.


845
01:04:24.860 --> 01:04:27.200
明天是星期三
Tomorrow is Wednesday.


846
01:04:27.200 --> 01:04:30.200
我要到监狱去了
I'm going back there, to the prison.


847
01:04:31.800 --> 01:04:34.140
他们到时候会让我见我爸爸的
They'll have to let me see him then.


848
01:04:55.330 --> 01:04:57.360
从现在开始 你就别出门了
From now on, you're staying inside.


849
01:04:57.360 --> 01:04:59.630
- 那么做太危险了 - 不 妈妈
- It's much too dangerous. - No, Mama-jan.


850
01:04:59.630 --> 01:05:01.830
- 我们会一起设法逃出来的 - “我们”？
- We manage all right out there. - "We"?


851
01:05:01.840 --> 01:05:05.770
我和德利瓦 她也是个女孩 我们一起工作
Me and Deliwar. She's a girl too. We work together.


852
01:05:05.770 --> 01:05:09.510
我们已经给我表兄写信了 让他们给你姐姐在马扎安排一门亲事
We've written to my cousin to arrange a marriage for your sister in Mazar


853
01:05:09.510 --> 01:05:11.640
他们回信表示同意
They wrote back, and it was accepted.


854
01:05:11.650 --> 01:05:14.510
后天会有人来把我们带走
Someone will come for us the day after tomorrow to take us away.


855
01:05:14.510 --> 01:05:16.410
- 你以后不用再冒险去监狱了 - 什么？
- You don't need to do this anymore. - What?


856
01:05:16.420 --> 01:05:18.420
这日子不能这么过
We can't go on like this.


857
01:05:18.420 --> 01:05:20.920
- 我们不能靠你养活啊 - 为什么？
- We can't depend on you to keep us alive. - Why?


858
01:05:20.920 --> 01:05:22.790
我现在挣的钱足够养家了
I provide for you just fine.


859
01:05:22.790 --> 01:05:24.960
这不是一个孩子的工作
It's not the job of a child.


860
01:05:24.960 --> 01:05:27.490
我们怎么能撇下爸爸离开
How can we leave without Baba?


861
01:05:27.490 --> 01:05:29.960
每天你回家的时候 身上都带着伤口
Every day you come home with cuts and blisters.


862
01:05:29.960 --> 01:05:33.670
每天你出去工作 我都不知能否看到你安然归来
Every day you go out there, and I don't know if I'll see you back again.


863
01:05:34.800 --> 01:05:36.800
我不能连你也失去
I can't lose you too.


864
01:05:36.800 --> 01:05:38.800
我不会去的
I'm not going.


865
01:05:38.800 --> 01:05:41.870
爸爸会回来的 我们走了 家里就没人等他了
Baba could come back, and no one will be here waiting for him.


866
01:05:41.880 --> 01:05:44.310
那我们要等多久
So how long should we wait?


867
01:05:44.310 --> 01:05:46.740
等到他们发现你是女孩 然后也把你从我身边夺走吗？
Until you're found out and taken away from me?


868
01:05:46.750 --> 01:05:48.980
等到我不得不把扎西送出去 来赚钱养家吗？
Until I have to send Zaki out to earn our keep?


869
01:05:48.980 --> 01:05:51.280
在我们离开之前 让我去看看他吧
Let me go see him before we leave.


870
01:05:51.280 --> 01:05:53.480
好让他知道我们要去的是哪
Let me tell him where we are going.


871
01:05:53.490 --> 01:05:55.890
- 帕尔瓦娜 - 让我帮他把手杖带上
- Parvana! - Let me bring him his walking stick.


872
01:05:55.890 --> 01:05:57.620
然后我就跟你走
Then I will go with you.


873
01:05:57.620 --> 01:06:01.560
我会做一个好妹妹 一个好女儿
Then I will be a good sister and a good daughter.


874
01:06:01.560 --> 01:06:03.160
我发誓
I promise.


875
01:06:03.960 --> 01:06:05.570
我保证
I promise.


876
01:06:20.650 --> 01:06:22.310
听话 不要走
Please don't go.


877
01:06:22.320 --> 01:06:24.880
听妈妈的吧  现在外面太危险了
Please, it is much too dangerous now.


878
01:06:24.880 --> 01:06:27.450
妈妈 我走了
Mama-jan, I'm going.


879
01:06:27.450 --> 01:06:29.320
宵禁之前我一定回来
I'll be back tonight before curfew.


880
01:06:29.320 --> 01:06:31.860
- 不要 苏莱曼 - 妈妈
- No, Sulayman. - Mama-jan.


881
01:06:31.860 --> 01:06:35.330
- 你赶不回来的 - 让她去吧
- You won't come back. - Let her go now.


882
01:06:35.330 --> 01:06:37.460
让帕瓦尔娜去吧
Let Parvana go.


883
01:06:44.670 --> 01:06:46.610
哦
Oh!


884
01:06:53.510 --> 01:06:55.620
帕瓦尔娜
Parvana.


885
01:07:31.650 --> 01:07:33.290
德利瓦
Deliwar!


886
01:07:34.720 --> 01:07:37.660
你差点把我吓死
You frightened me half to death.


887
01:07:37.660 --> 01:07:39.660
我一直在到处找你
I've been looking for you everywhere.


888
01:07:39.660 --> 01:07:42.590
找我干嘛？想跟我一起去柴家商店干活吗？
Why? You want to work at the chai shop with me this morning?


889
01:07:42.590 --> 01:07:46.500
- 不 我不行 - 嘿 你想给扎西弄些糖果吗？
- No, I can't. - Hey, you want some candy for Zaki?


890
01:07:46.500 --> 01:07:49.340
明天我们就要离开喀布尔
We are leaving Kabul tomorrow.


891
01:07:50.940 --> 01:07:52.800
你要离开我吗？
You are leaving me?


892
01:07:52.810 --> 01:07:55.940
家里都安排好了 我也无能为力
It's been arranged. There's nothing I can do.


893
01:07:55.940 --> 01:08:00.080
我姐姐就要去马札里沙里夫结婚了
My sister is getting married in Mazar-e-Sharif.


894
01:08:00.080 --> 01:08:01.680
我还要再去一次监狱
I'm going back to the prison.


895
01:08:01.680 --> 01:08:03.680
我找到了一个能帮我的人
I found someone who can help me,


896
01:08:03.680 --> 01:08:05.920
而且我需要更多的钱来贿赂看守
and I need to get more money to bribe the guard.


897
01:08:05.920 --> 01:08:07.820
今天是最后期限了
I'll need it today.


898
01:08:07.820 --> 01:08:10.990
你只会挨更多拳头的 这个想法很愚蠢
You'll just get another punch in the guts. It's a stupid idea.


899
01:08:10.990 --> 01:08:12.820
这次不会的
I won't let that happen this time.


900
01:08:12.830 --> 01:08:15.960
- 我说了这个想法很愚蠢 - 求你了帮帮我吧
- I said it's a stupid idea. - Please help me.


901
01:08:15.960 --> 01:08:17.830
你想让我怎么做？
What do you want me to do?


902
01:08:17.830 --> 01:08:21.100
像你的儿童故事里那样 用魔法变出一些钱来给你吗？
Magic some money into your hand like in your kids' stories?


903
01:08:21.100 --> 01:08:23.800
那是行不通的 帕瓦尔娜
It doesn't work like that, Parvana.


904
01:08:23.800 --> 01:08:25.770
我帮不了你
I can't help you.


905
01:08:25.770 --> 01:08:29.870
赶紧逃到马札里沙里夫 然后享受那美好的婚礼吧
Now run away to Mazar-e-Sharif and have a nice wedding party.


906
01:08:29.880 --> 01:08:33.980
也许他们也会给你配个丈夫 你的麻烦就都不存在了
Maybe they'll find a husband for you too and your troubles will be over.


907
01:08:33.980 --> 01:08:36.410
至少能挺到婚礼结束
Until after the wedding, at least.


908
01:08:36.420 --> 01:08:37.850
你这个傻瓜
You fool!


909
01:08:40.990 --> 01:08:42.660
德利瓦
Deliwar!


910
01:08:43.720 --> 01:08:45.360
什沃吉亚
Shauzia.


911
01:08:53.870 --> 01:08:56.000
什沃吉亚
Shauzia.


912
01:08:56.000 --> 01:08:57.930
和我们一起走吧
Come with us.


913
01:08:57.940 --> 01:09:00.470
我不能
I can't.


914
01:09:00.470 --> 01:09:03.610
我爸爸会一直追到马札然后杀了我的
My father would come all the way to Mazar to kill me.


915
01:09:05.480 --> 01:09:08.480
我不能就这样离开喀布尔 帕瓦尔娜
I can't leave Kabul, Parvana, not like this.


916
01:09:10.680 --> 01:09:13.420
- 这儿 拿着 - 我不能拿你的钱
- Here, take this. - I can't take your money.


917
01:09:13.420 --> 01:09:15.390
你就拿着吧
Please take it.


918
01:09:18.490 --> 01:09:20.890
去看你爸爸吧
Go and see your Baba.


919
01:09:20.890 --> 01:09:24.960
告诉他 他有一个好女儿
Tell him that his daughter is a good daughter.


920
01:09:24.960 --> 01:09:28.640
告诉他 德利瓦说的
Tell him that Deliwar said so.


921
01:09:34.910 --> 01:09:37.640
嘿 德利瓦
Hey, Deliwar.


922
01:09:37.640 --> 01:09:39.780
怎么了？
What?


923
01:09:39.780 --> 01:09:42.510
20年后的今天 就在你之前提过的
I'll meet you at that beach you were talking about,


924
01:09:42.520 --> 01:09:45.180
那片月亮牵引海水的沙滩上
where the moon pulls the water,


925
01:09:45.180 --> 01:09:47.080
我等待和你再次相遇

926
01:09:47.090 --> 01:09:50.220
我想那时我会认不出你来的 奥狄什
I don't think I'll recognize you then, Aatish.


927
01:09:50.220 --> 01:09:54.430
好吧 那你可以优惠卖我些漂亮的蓝石头
Well, you can sell me some pretty blue stones for a great price.


928
01:09:56.460 --> 01:09:58.530
后会有期
Until next time then.


929
01:10:01.530 --> 01:10:03.800
后会有期
Until next time.


930
01:10:21.850 --> 01:10:24.090
真主保佑你 你是费特马吗？
Peace be upon you. Are you Fattema?


931
01:10:24.090 --> 01:10:25.290
是的 我是费特马
Yes, I am Fattema.


932
01:10:25.290 --> 01:10:28.560
我是你的二表哥 穆罕默德·阿卜杜尔派我从马柞过来
I am your second cousin. Mohammed Abdul sent me from Mazar.


933
01:10:28.560 --> 01:10:30.930
叫上你的家人一起 我们现在就得走了
Gather your family. We must leave immediately.


934
01:10:30.930 --> 01:10:34.700
不 你看 你不应该这么早就来的
No, you see, you weren't supposed to come so soon.


935
01:10:34.700 --> 01:10:37.240
我儿子不在 我们必须等他回来
My son is away. We must wait for him to return.


936
01:10:37.240 --> 01:10:39.000
仗马上就打过来了 你没听说吗？
There is a war coming. Have you not heard?


937
01:10:39.010 --> 01:10:41.110
我们必须赶在他们封路之前离开
We have to leave now before they block the roads.


938
01:10:41.110 --> 01:10:43.870
我们必须等到她回家 我得等我的女儿
We have to wait until she comes home. I have to wait for my daughter.


939
01:10:43.880 --> 01:10:46.180
儿子？女儿？到底是哪一个？
Son? Daughter? Which is it?


940
01:10:46.180 --> 01:10:48.040
收拾东西 我们现在就要出发
Gather your things. We are leaving now!


941
01:10:48.050 --> 01:10:50.950
帕尔瓦娜回来前我是不会走的 我们必须等她回来
I'm not leaving without Parvana. We have to wait.


942
01:10:50.950 --> 01:10:52.950
我带你走已经算你走运的了 老女人
Count yourself lucky I'm taking you, old woman.


943
01:10:52.950 --> 01:10:54.950
这个女孩和那个孩子可更有价值
The girl and the baby are of more worth.


944
01:10:54.950 --> 01:10:56.850
我这趟可不能白来
I didn't come all this way for nothing.


945
01:10:56.860 --> 01:10:59.290
要是现在不走 我们就无法离开这里了
If we do not go now, we won't get out of here at all.


946
01:10:59.290 --> 01:11:01.830
- 我的宝贝 把他给我 - 快跟我走
- My baby! Give him to me! - Let's go! Argh!


947
01:11:01.830 --> 01:11:03.730
扎西 扎西
Zaki! Zaki!


948
01:11:04.760 --> 01:11:07.300
把孩子给我 把他给我
Give me my baby. Give him to me!


949
01:11:07.300 --> 01:11:09.470
- 不要 把他给我 - 放开 放开
- No! Give him to me! - Let go! Let go!


950
01:11:24.620 --> 01:11:26.880
- 问安 孩子 - 问安
- Salaam, little one. - Salaam.


951
01:11:26.890 --> 01:11:30.190
你带着一根老人的拐杖打算去哪？
Where are you going to with an old man's stick?


952
01:11:30.190 --> 01:11:32.790
这是我爸爸的
It belongs to my Baba.


953
01:11:32.790 --> 01:11:35.760
我要带给他 到监狱里
I'm taking it to him, to the prison.


954
01:11:36.900 --> 01:11:38.530
我知道了
I see.


955
01:11:39.300 --> 01:11:41.530
我们顺路
We're going that way.


956
01:11:48.710 --> 01:11:50.340
把我的孩子给我
Give me my baby!


957
01:11:50.340 --> 01:11:53.880
- 快跟我走 如果你还想要这孩子 就跟我走 - 扎西
- Let's go! If you want to keep the baby, come with me! - Zaki!


958
01:11:53.880 --> 01:11:55.910
我女儿还在外面
My daughter is out there.


959
01:11:55.920 --> 01:11:58.320
那你为什么会愚蠢到让她一个人出去呢？
Then what kind of fool are you to have sent her out alone?


960
01:11:58.320 --> 01:12:01.220
上车 否则你今天可不止会失去一个孩子
Get in, or she won't be the only child you'll lose today!


961
01:12:01.220 --> 01:12:04.020
不要...把我的孩子给我
Don't... Give me my baby!


962
01:12:04.020 --> 01:12:05.920
叫这孩子别吵
Keep him quiet!


963
01:12:05.930 --> 01:12:07.890
我求你了
I am begging you.


964
01:12:07.890 --> 01:12:12.800
等等我的女儿
Wait for my daughter!


965
01:13:00.010 --> 01:13:03.250
来吧 苏拉娅 我们得生火了
Come, Soraya. We must start a fire.


966
01:13:05.050 --> 01:13:06.850
我找罗山
I am looking for Roshan.


967
01:13:06.850 --> 01:13:09.190
嘿 我找罗山
Hey! I am looking for Roshan.


968
01:13:09.190 --> 01:13:12.660
我找罗山 我找罗山
I am looking for Roshan. I am looking for Roshan.


969
01:13:12.660 --> 01:13:15.890
我找罗山 我找罗山
I am looking for Roshan. I am looking for Roshan.


970
01:13:15.890 --> 01:13:18.090
- 开门  - 离门远一点 你这笨蛋
- Open the door! - Get away from the door, you stupid kid!


971
01:13:18.100 --> 01:13:20.360
- 我找罗山  - 快滚
- I am looking for Roshan! - Get out of here!


972
01:13:20.370 --> 01:13:22.330
- 我找罗山- 你是傻子吗？
- I am looking for Roshan! - Are you stupid?


973
01:13:22.340 --> 01:13:23.930
- 我找罗山 - 闭嘴
- I am looking for Roshan. - Shut up!


974
01:13:23.940 --> 01:13:25.300
你在这干什么呢？
What are you doing here?


975
01:13:25.300 --> 01:13:28.240
没事了 他是我儿子
It's all right. He's my son.


976
01:13:28.240 --> 01:13:30.740
里边需要你
You're wanted inside.


977
01:13:32.440 --> 01:13:34.380
这个男孩欠一些管教
That boy needs some discipline.


978
01:13:34.380 --> 01:13:36.180
那是我的事
That's my business.


979
01:13:39.150 --> 01:13:42.950
我的真主啊 你来这干什么？
What in the name of the merciful are you doing here?


980
01:13:42.960 --> 01:13:46.420
今天是星期三 我来找你的表弟罗山
It's Wednesday. I've come to meet your cousin Roshan.


981
01:13:46.430 --> 01:13:49.690
那边已经开战了
There's a war started.


982
01:13:49.700 --> 01:13:51.830
罗山已参战去了
Roshan has gone to fight.


983
01:13:51.830 --> 01:13:56.100
我们被从城里带到监狱 来清除那些不愿为我们战斗的人
We've been brought from the city to clear the prison of anyone who won't fight for us.


984
01:13:57.340 --> 01:13:59.140
- 那个老师... - 他还活着吗？
- The teacher... - Is he alive?


985
01:13:59.140 --> 01:14:00.800
我不知道
I don't know.


986
01:14:00.810 --> 01:14:04.910
那个老师是我的父亲 我是帕尔瓦纳 他的女儿
The teacher is my father. I am Parvana, his daughter.


987
01:14:06.050 --> 01:14:08.720
救救他吧 求你了
Help him, please.


988
01:14:10.950 --> 01:14:14.080
太阳下山前我还没回来的话 你就赶紧跑
If I'm not back before the sun has gone down, you run.


989
01:14:14.090 --> 01:14:17.860
能跑多远就跑多远 千万不要停
Run as far away as you can from here and you keep on running.


990
01:14:17.860 --> 01:14:20.220
日落之后你绝不能待在这里 你明白吗？
You can't stay here after sunset. Do you understand?


991
01:14:20.230 --> 01:14:21.760
- 谢谢你 - 你明白了吗？
- Thank you. - Do you understand?


992
01:14:21.760 --> 01:14:23.890
- 是的 - 在那之前 你先藏起来
- Yes. - Hide yourself until then.


993
01:14:35.840 --> 01:14:39.940
从前有一个叫苏莱曼的男孩
Once there was a young boy called Sulayman.


994
01:14:39.950 --> 01:14:42.910
他知道他命中注定要为人民服务
He knew his heart was fated to serve his people,


995
01:14:42.920 --> 01:14:44.950
但他快没时间了
and he was running out of time.


996
01:14:53.860 --> 01:14:57.360
谢谢你 太谢谢你了
Thank you. Thank you so much.


997
01:14:57.360 --> 01:15:00.900
- 来吧 上车 - 我们得回去找我的女儿
- Come on! Get in the car. - We have to go back for my daughter.


998
01:15:00.900 --> 01:15:03.700
我说了 赶紧过来
I said come here. Now!


999
01:15:04.370 --> 01:15:06.300
我们不会跟你走的
We're not going with you.


1000
01:15:06.310 --> 01:15:08.110
妈妈？
Mama-jan?


1001
01:15:08.110 --> 01:15:11.210
你 过来 听不见我说话吗？
You, come now! Do you hear me?


1002
01:15:11.210 --> 01:15:14.980
让你过来你就过来
You come here like I told you to!


1003
01:15:16.180 --> 01:15:18.980
你现在就过来
You come now!


1004
01:15:20.120 --> 01:15:23.850
我们不会和你走的 你开车离开吧
We will not go with you. Just drive away from us.


1005
01:15:23.860 --> 01:15:27.190
上车 快上车
Get in the car. Get in the car now!


1006
01:15:27.190 --> 01:15:29.330
妈妈
Mama-jan!


1007
01:15:33.830 --> 01:15:37.000
苏莱曼 苏莱曼
Sulayman! Sulayman!


1008
01:15:38.540 --> 01:15:40.870
勇敢点 苏莱曼
Be brave, Sulayman.


1009
01:16:31.360 --> 01:16:33.120
快跑 苏拉娅
Run, Soraya.


1010
01:16:33.130 --> 01:16:35.330
- 现在带着扎西快跑  - 妈妈
- Take Zaki and run now! - Mama!


1011
01:16:35.330 --> 01:16:37.360
快走 一直跑
Go! Keep running!


1012
01:16:42.030 --> 01:16:46.070
你..让我们..走
You... let... us... go.


1013
01:16:56.650 --> 01:16:58.550
开门
Open the door.


1014
01:16:58.550 --> 01:17:00.020
你背着那个人干什么？
What are you doing with that?


1015
01:17:00.020 --> 01:17:03.820
他已经死了 我要把他和其他尸体放在一起 开门 让我过去
He's dead. I'm putting him with the others. Open the door. Let me through.


1016
01:17:18.640 --> 01:17:20.340
- 都快点走  - 站住
- Move, move, move, move, move! - Stop!


1017
01:17:20.340 --> 01:17:23.910
- 所有人 排成一行 - 站住
- Line up. All of you, all of you. - Stop!


1018
01:17:23.910 --> 01:17:25.480
我说了 站住
I said stop!


1019
01:17:25.480 --> 01:17:27.650
天快要黑了
It will be dark soon.


1020
01:17:27.650 --> 01:17:30.250
拉扎克
Razaq?


1021
01:17:30.250 --> 01:17:32.250
拉扎克？ 拉扎克？
Razaq? Razaq?


1022
01:17:43.630 --> 01:17:45.600
苏莱曼
Sulayman.


1023
01:17:45.600 --> 01:17:47.870
苏莱曼
Sulayman.


1024
01:17:48.400 --> 01:17:49.670
镜子可以反射光！
The mirror shines!


1025
01:17:49.670 --> 01:17:52.010
闪瞎那些怪物
Use it to blind the jaguars!


1026
01:18:04.320 --> 01:18:07.420
然后用网罩住他们
The net ensnares! Throw it over them!


1027
01:18:07.420 --> 01:18:09.890
哈
Hah!


1028
01:18:44.760 --> 01:18:47.220
拉扎克 拉扎克
Razaq. Razaq!


1029
01:18:47.230 --> 01:18:50.060
拉扎克 我来找我的父亲
Razaq! I have come for my father.


1030
01:18:50.060 --> 01:18:51.970
我来找我的父亲
I have come for my Baba!


1031
01:18:52.600 --> 01:18:55.100
把他放下来
Put him down!


1032
01:18:55.100 --> 01:18:57.200
我说了把他放下
I said put him down.


1033
01:19:02.570 --> 01:19:05.210
你了解现在的状况吗？
Do you see what is happening?


1034
01:19:05.210 --> 01:19:08.450
你把他带到哪里去？ 谁在外面？
Where are you taking him? Who's out there?


1035
01:19:08.450 --> 01:19:11.050
你就不能睁一只眼闭一只眼吗？
Look away, can't you?


1036
01:19:11.050 --> 01:19:13.220
现在这么乱 放过这个男人又能如何？
It is just one man. What does it matter?


1037
01:19:17.020 --> 01:19:19.620
走
Go.


1038
01:19:19.630 --> 01:19:21.420
走
Go!


1039
01:19:21.430 --> 01:19:23.360
走 除非你要杀了我
Go, unless you're going to kill me.


1040
01:19:27.070 --> 01:19:29.730
我会尖叫并诅咒你
I will scream and curse you


1041
01:19:29.730 --> 01:19:33.740
直到我用尽最后一口气
until the last breath leaves my body.


1042
01:19:33.740 --> 01:19:35.440
来吧
Go.


1043
01:19:38.680 --> 01:19:41.510
你疯了 疯了
You're crazy. Crazy.


1044
01:19:43.110 --> 01:19:45.350
你死在这都与我无关
You can die out here for all I care.


1045
01:19:45.780 --> 01:19:47.120
去死吧
Die.


1046
01:20:10.780 --> 01:20:12.550
苏莱曼
Sulayman.


1047
01:20:13.610 --> 01:20:15.220
苏莱曼
Sulayman.


1048
01:20:16.420 --> 01:20:17.680
苏莱曼
Sulayman.


1049
01:20:24.860 --> 01:20:27.290
我不是来杀你的
I have not come to kill you.


1050
01:20:38.100 --> 01:20:39.840
苏莱曼
Sulayman!


1051
01:20:39.840 --> 01:20:41.570
用你的故事让他平静下来
Soothe him with your story,


1052
01:20:41.570 --> 01:20:44.370
那个妈妈从没说起过的故事
the one that Mama-jan can't speak of.


1053
01:20:44.380 --> 01:20:45.810
告诉他
Tell him.


1054
01:20:45.810 --> 01:20:47.710
苏莱曼
Sulayman!


1055
01:20:47.710 --> 01:20:49.710
我叫苏莱曼
My name is Sulayman.


1056
01:20:49.720 --> 01:20:51.820
告诉他发生了什么
Tell him what happened.


1057
01:20:51.820 --> 01:20:54.490
告诉他你的故事
Tell him your story.


1058
01:20:54.490 --> 01:20:55.850
我叫苏莱曼
My name is Sulayman.


1059
01:20:55.850 --> 01:20:58.160
我的母亲是一个作家
My mother is a writer.


1060
01:20:58.160 --> 01:20:59.890
我父亲是一个老师
My father is a teacher.


1061
01:20:59.890 --> 01:21:03.430
我的妹妹们总在争吵
And my sisters always fight each other.


1062
01:21:03.430 --> 01:21:05.830
有天我在街上发现一个玩具
One day I found a toy on the street.


1063
01:21:05.830 --> 01:21:07.800
就把它捡了起来
I picked it up.


1064
01:21:07.800 --> 01:21:09.530
它爆炸了
It exploded.


1065
01:21:11.240 --> 01:21:13.870
我不记得后面发生了什么
I don't remember what happened after that


1066
01:21:13.870 --> 01:21:15.670
因为这就是结局
because it was the end.


1067
01:21:15.670 --> 01:21:18.710
起作用了 苏莱曼 继续讲 继续跟他讲
It's working, Sulayman! Tell him. Tell him!


