象王对男孩的态度发生了转变
The Elephant was transformed.


1087
01:22:10.530 --> 01:22:12.930
他从山峦中拿出那袋种子
He took the bag of seed from the center of the mountain


1088
01:22:12.930 --> 01:22:15.500
还给了苏莱曼
and gave it back to Sulayman.


1089
01:22:15.500 --> 01:22:18.500
苏莱曼回到他的家乡
Sulayman returned to his village.


1090
01:22:18.500 --> 01:22:21.740
村民们载歌载舞
There was much dancing and singing


1091
01:22:21.740 --> 01:22:24.310
开怀大吃
and laughing and eating.


1092
01:22:31.750 --> 01:22:33.420
拉扎克？
Razaq?


1093
01:22:39.660 --> 01:22:40.920
爸爸？
Baba?


1094
01:22:40.930 --> 01:22:43.560
爸爸  他还活着吗？
Baba! Is he alive?


1095
01:22:44.960 --> 01:22:48.460
这不是他的血 他还活着
It is not his blood. He lives.


1096
01:23:08.890 --> 01:23:11.660
离开这里 孩子 快走吧
Get out of here now, child. Go on.


1097
01:23:11.660 --> 01:23:14.330
全速离开此地
As fast as you can.


1098
01:24:18.020 --> 01:24:19.820
这是月亮
It's the moon.


1099
01:24:27.030 --> 01:24:28.670
苏拉娅
Soraya.


1100
01:24:29.600 --> 01:24:32.800
苏……拉娅
S... Sora... Soraya!


1101
01:24:32.810 --> 01:24:35.040
