- Mama? - Soraya!


1102
01:24:35.040 --> 01:24:37.410
苏……
So...


1103
01:24:42.010 --> 01:24:46.320
在我们家乡 人才是最无价的珍宝
We are a land whose people are its greatest treasure.


1104
01:24:50.690 --> 01:24:54.690
我们的家乡是在两个交战国的边境交汇处
We are at the edges of empires at war with each other.


1105
01:24:57.030 --> 01:24:58.670
帕尔……
Par...


1106
01:25:00.700 --> 01:25:02.630
帕尔瓦娜
Parvana.


1107
01:25:04.400 --> 01:25:08.740
我们的家园在兴都库什山脉的利爪下被分成数个部分
We are a fractured land in the claws of the Hindu Kush mountains,


1108
01:25:08.740 --> 01:25:12.310
有北部沙漠那炽烈之眼的灼热
scorched by the fiery eyes of the northern deserts.


1109
01:25:13.610 --> 01:25:17.780
亦包括那黑白交汇的冰峰之凛冽
Black rubble earth against ice peaks.


1110
01:25:19.390 --> 01:25:22.850
我们的家园叫阿里亚纳
We are Ariana,


1111
01:25:22.850 --> 01:25:25.790
是高尚之乡
the land of the noble.


1112
01:25:27.160 --> 01:25:30.790
话要说的更有道理 而不是提高音量
Raise your words, not your voice.


1113
01:25:30.800 --> 01:25:34.000
毕竟是雨水滋润花朵生长
It is rain that makes the flowers grow,


1114
01:25:34.000 --> 01:25:36.400
而不是雷鸣
not thunder.